## Specs-T1 [G8] useGateInbox snooze — snoozed gate reappears after timeout
**Status:** done
**Test File:** `packages/auto-forge-ui/tests/unit/useGateInbox.spec.ts`
**Tags:** stack:frontend
**Depends on:** Chat-G1, Relay-D6

```typescript
const inbox = useGateInbox()
inbox.registerGate(gateA)
```

1. Call `inbox.snoozeGate(gateA.id, 0.1)` (100ms for test)
2. Assert active secretary is null
3. Wait 150ms
4. Assert gateA is back as active




