## Specs-T4 [G21] GoalsTable renders hierarchical tree with toggle interaction
**Status:** draft
**Test File:** `frontend/src/components/category/GoalsTable.vue` (component test)
**Tags:** stack:frontend
**Depends on:** Specs-G7, Specs-D4

1. Render `GoalsTable` with parent goal `Chat-G1` and sub-goal `Chat-G2`
2. Assert `Chat-G1` row has `.node-toggle-area` (has children)
3. Assert `Chat-G2` row has `.node-indent` but no `.node-toggle-area`
4. Click toggle area on `Chat-G1` → assert `Chat-G2` row appears in DOM
5. Click toggle area again → assert `Chat-G2` row removed from DOM
6. Click `Chat-G1` row (outside toggle) → assert `@open-detail` emitted with `Chat-G1`

