## Specs-T5 [G21] GoalDetailModal opens, edits, and closes correctly
**Status:** draft
**Test File:** `frontend/src/components/GoalDetailModal.vue` (component test)
**Tags:** stack:frontend
**Depends on:** Specs-G7, Specs-D5

1. Render `GoalDetailModal` with a goal item
2. Assert modal overlay and card are present
3. Assert header shows ID badge and title
4. Assert meta bar shows priority, status, and tag chips
5. Assert RelationsPanel rendered in body
6. Click "Edit" button → assert `@edit` emitted, `GoalEditor` mounts
7. Press ESC → assert `@close` emitted
8. Click overlay backdrop → assert `@close` emitted
9. Click modal card → assert no `@close` emitted (click.stop)

