## Specs-T6 [G21] Sidebar Stack/Module filters apply AND logic
**Status:** draft
**Test File:** `frontend/src/views/SpecsView.vue` (component test)
**Tags:** stack:frontend
**Depends on:** Specs-G7, Specs-D6

1. Render `SpecsView` with mixed-tag items (stack:frontend+module:specs, stack:backend+module:relay)
2. Select "frontend" in Stack drawer → assert only frontend items shown
3. Also select "specs" in Module drawer → assert only frontend+specs items shown
4. Deselect all Module tags → assert all frontend items shown (stack filter only)
5. Deselect all Stack tags → assert all items shown (no filters)
6. Select a non-matching combination → assert empty state shown

