## Specs-T7 [G21] Tag badges display shortened color-coded values
**Status:** draft
**Test File:** `frontend/src/components/category/GoalsTable.vue` (component test)
**Tags:** stack:frontend
**Depends on:** Specs-G7, Specs-D6

1. Render `GoalsTable` with item tagged `stack:frontend, module:specs`
2. Assert tag chips show text "frontend" and "specs" (not full `kind:value`)
3. Assert `stack` chip has `.tag-stack` class (blue styling)
4. Assert `module` chip has `.tag-module` class (purple styling)
5. Hover chip → assert `title` attribute contains full tag text `stack:frontend`
6. Add 3+ tags → assert only first 2 render inline, overflow shows `+N`
